We are very pleased to announce that Zheng Shen will be joining us as our postdoctoral researcher from May 1st 2018.
Zheng wrote his PhD thesis entitled *Feature Arithmetic in the Nominal Domain* at the University of Connecticut, before coming to Frankfurt working as the postdoctoral assistant in the Graduiertenkolleg `Nominal Modification'.

We are very pleased that he will be joining our project. Welcome, Zheng!